'''Dr. Dinah L. Moché''' ([[October 24]], [[1936]] &ndash; [[May 22]], [[2018]])<ref>{{WebCite|url=https://ballarddurand.com/obit/dinah-l-moche|text=Ballard-Durand Funeral & Cremation Services|archivedate=20210202071208}}</ref> was Professor of Physics and Astronomy at the City University of New York and writer of many books about astronomy. She has sold over 10 million copies in 7 languages worldwide.

Dr. Moché wrote ''[[The Star Wars Question and Answer Book About Space]]'', published by [[Random House]] in [[1979]].

